  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/2000",
  "title": "chore(dev): reload in dev now takes ~500ms",
  "body": "Before this commit, the `yarn start` workflow took 10s when a file was CHANGED (not even talking about the 40s boot time), now it takes 500ms in average for a reload. Which is good.\r\n\r\nOptimization was done via:\r\n- webpack 2 switch\r\n- dev env uses simpler sourcemap strategy\r\n- use happypack (https://github.com/amireh/happypack)\r\n- Create a common chunks plugin (this reduces the size of downloaded\r\nJavaScript files by a big factor).\r\n\r\nFlow example: load, one save, another save.\r\n\r\nBefore:\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/23194452/004d18e2-f863-11e6-8ed4-18c32883c1af.png)\r\n\r\nStartup took ~50s. Saves took ~10s each.\r\n\r\nAfter:\r\n\r\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/123822/23194507/59bd95e6-f863-11e6-8b7e-7fcd263d647d.png)\r\n\r\nStartup took ~30s. Saves took ~500ms (Ok FIRST save took 2s, but trust me, every other took 500ms)",
